VERSION 1.1.3 - 2022-10-12
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Handled potential for null being returned when validating a banned domain name


VERSION 1.1.2 - 2022-10-11
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changed banned domain check to use pattern matching for more robust validation including subdomains


